name: The Rebel
description: After Hell's invasion of Earth, mankind had no adequate way to react and started to succumb, slowly yet inexorably. More and more people were enslaved by the Netherworld forces each day, deprived of their will to become faithful and mindless servants of the Dark God Baphomet, in the form of 'Cultists'. But one day, one not-so-plagued man dares to oppose...
